csw.params.core.states

Class DemandState

  • java.lang.Object
    • csw.params.core.generics.ParameterSetType<DemandState>
      • csw.params.core.states.DemandState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterSetKeyData, TMTSerializable, java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product

    public class DemandState
extends ParameterSetType<DemandState>
implements ParameterSetKeyData, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    A state variable that indicates the ''demand'' or requested state.

    param: prefix identifies the target subsystem param: stateName identifies the name of the state param: paramSet an optional initial set of items (keys with values)
